text: You can see it as valuable to yourself and to someone else, it’s isn’t a binary choice.
Sorry to hear that.  But I’m sure if you do decide to go, you won’t regret the decision, I certainly didn’t.  I wouldn’t be where I am today if I hadn’t gotten my master’s.
Yeah, I also think part of the reason is that his base is made mostly of people who supported Bernie in 2016, and they resent that.
